{
  "stem": "3988.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And maybe he didn't use the shovel right, you know, put enough dirt, enough coal, you know, on the shovel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They pulled them out, and bang bang, and shot them, you know, right there, in front.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I figured, I-- you know, as long as I can work, I just have to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe this will save me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I worked as-- and some of the guys, you know-- like in the coal mines, you see, you get a little lamp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know what you call it, but a little lam.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, you go down the coal mine and it's dark.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's how you work by, by this little thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the wood posts, you know to holding up the ceiling-- and what you did with the lamp, you know, you hit it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, it had a hook.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you put the little lamp on that hook.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you worked by there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You see, and that's the light you had there, right there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the foreman could stay a little bit, a few feet away, so you cannot see him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But he can see you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because it's dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And if he sees, you know, some guy doesn't perform, he doesn't work the way it is, he just walked up to him and said, hey, you didn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Or he beat the shit out of him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Or he shot him-- you know, killed him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And used to get him up, you know, on stretchers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Some guys never made it up-- you know, went down and never made it up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no-- a few hundred in that particular, you know, Jaworzno.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then stayed there and till the Russians start coming in, the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What time what?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
